name: rov-dive-products-dataset-for-ex1502l3-caribbean-exploration-rov-on-noaa-ship-okeanos-explorer-
notes: Dataset of folders containing ROV dive products for each ROV dive performed during EX1502L3. The files within the folder are text, image, graph, comma-separated value files representing the ROV track, the ROV profile, the images along the track, the events noted along the track.
